_sText:
This is my first project in Hammer editor. My main idea while making this was to do something that looks cool. As a result, the map is better for looking at it than for playing. Next time I'll try to focus more on playability than aesthetic. Characteristics - 64 slots
- 3D Skybox
- Night theme
- Color Correction
Hope you find it gorgeous, sir. Note to my self: wow, making maps is so slow.
